Day 14/14: Net worth affects - summary and conclusions

I was curious about whether my net worth ($4.5k at the time) could affect the algorithm to enhance my ranking and the exposure of my posts without a big reward pool.

So, I decided to try something for 12 days (originally planned to be 14 days). Each day, I added a small amount to my net worth (0.25 $BTC) and shared daily updates with a very small reward ($0.1). Then, I watched closely to see if anything would change.

Now, let's take a look at what happened during my experiment!

🧵 👇

Day 13/14: Net worth affects

Yesterday marked the final transfer, and I am currently compiling data for a detailed summary thread that will be published tomorrow.

The ranking is holding steady, currently at 3099 from 3105. Followers have increased slightly, but many of them lack real engagement.
